WEBVTT

00:04:56.141 --> 00:05:02.933
So, you know, we should end up
not having the 1918 flu situation.

00:05:03.402 --> 00:05:05.690
We should be able to do
a lot better than that.

00:05:07.280 --> 00:05:10.100
CA: And that's because of actions
that we would take.

00:05:10.124 --> 00:05:13.926
I mean, left without the right actions,

00:05:13.950 --> 00:05:15.913
the prospects are pretty deadly.

00:05:15.937 --> 00:05:19.866
If we knew what we knew in 1919,

00:05:19.890 --> 00:05:22.339
this thing could take out
tens of millions of people

00:05:22.363 --> 00:05:23.513
around the world.

00:05:24.371 --> 00:05:25.553
You said --

00:05:25.577 --> 00:05:29.755
is the key thing here that it's got
this sort of a strange combination

00:05:29.779 --> 00:05:32.379
of being certainly
more dangerous than flu --